## `/transcript` ‚Äî Process Meeting Notes

When the user types **`/transcript`** or pastes a meeting transcript, analyze and extract actionable information.

### Input Formats

| Format | Example |
|--------|---------|
| Trigger then paste | `/transcript` followed by pasted text |
| Inline with context | `/transcript 1:1 with Lisa` then paste |
| File reference | `/transcript file:meeting_notes.txt` |
| Quick mode | `/transcript quick` ‚Äî extract action items only |

### Processing Flow

#### Step 1: Identify Meeting Context

Prompt (if not provided):
```
