#### Step 3: Extract Action Items

Scan for patterns indicating follow-ups:

| Pattern | Example | Extraction |
|---------|---------|------------|
| "I'll..." / "I will..." | "I'll send that doc" | ‚Üí (Self) follow-up |
| "[Name] will..." | "Lisa will update the widget" | ‚Üí Follow-up for [Name] |
| "Can you..." / "Could you..." | "Can you check on that?" | ‚Üí Follow-up for speaker's target |
| "Action item:" | "Action item: review metrics" | ‚Üí Explicit follow-up |
| "Let's..." / "We should..." | "Let's circle back on this" | ‚Üí (Self) follow-up |
| "By [date]..." | "By Friday, we need..." | ‚Üí Follow-up with deadline |
| "Follow up on..." | "Follow up on the ticket" | ‚Üí Explicit follow-up |

Output format:
```
