```

#### Step 4: Extract Decisions

Scan for decision patterns:

| Pattern | Example |
|---------|---------|
| "We decided..." | "We decided to go with option A" |
| "The decision is..." | "The decision is to delay launch" |
| "We're going to..." | "We're going to use the new API" |
| "Approved:" | "Approved: new vendor contract" |
| "Agreement:" | "Agreement: weekly syncs instead of daily" |
| "Final call:" | "Final call: ship it Friday" |

