Log these decisions? (y/all/select by number)
```

#### Step 5: Extract Hot Topics & Escalations

Scan for risk/escalation patterns:

| Pattern | Example |
|---------|---------|
| "Blocked by..." | "We're blocked by the API team" |
| "Risk:" / "At risk:" | "This is at risk if we don't get resources" |
| "Escalate..." | "We need to escalate this to leadership" |
| "Concern:" | "My concern is the timeline" |
| "Issue:" | "The issue is budget approval" |

Output format:
```
