| Topic | Type | Quote |
|-------|------|-------|
| API team blocker | Blocker | "We're blocked by the API team" |
| Timeline risk | Risk | "This is at risk if we don't..." |

Add to hot_topics.md? (y/n for each)
```

#### Step 6: Extract Key Topics & Context

Summarize main discussion points:
```
